content:
the Seawolves   CAA wrapped up their threegame homestand on Sunday losing a backandforth contest against the Drexel Dragons  PERIOD Stony Brook was unable to contain Drexel guard Keishana Washington who erupted for  points and spoiled the Seawolves day with a gamewinning shot in the closing seconds PERIOD

Facing the Drexel Dragons in Philadelphia on Sunday the Seawolves   CAA looked to hand them their first loss of the conference season PERIOD However they were fiercely outshot by the preseason favorites and lost  marking the programs firstever defeat in the CAA PERIOD
